you can then share on Facebook or YouTube.

00:02:55.450 --> 00:02:59.669
Having cameras in our phones is great and
makes video accessible, but sometimes that

00:02:59.669 --> 00:03:05.159
shakiness is just terrible! Steadycam Pro
is an iPhone 4 application that aims to fix

00:03:05.159 --> 00:03:11.169
that issue. Instead of carrying around a physical
steadicam, they’re fixing it WHILE you shoot.

00:03:11.169 --> 00:03:15.200
It looks like it works well, but I haven’t
tried it myself - don’t have that fancy

00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:20.480
